{"query":"rest-related","translation":"休息に関連する","related_terms":[{"term":"rest","translation":"休息","definition":"活動を停止して、心身を休めること。","part_of_speech":"名詞、動詞"},{"term":"relaxation","translation":"リラックス","definition":"心身の緊張をほぐし、くつろぐこと。","part_of_speech":"名詞"},{"term":"sleep","translation":"睡眠","definition":"意識を失い、生理機能を維持するために必要な休息。","part_of_speech":"名詞、動詞"},{"term":"vacation","translation":"休暇","definition":"仕事や学校などを休んで、旅行やレジャーを楽しむ期間。","part_of_speech":"名詞"},{"term":"holiday","translation":"休日","definition":"法律や慣習で定められた、仕事や学校を休む日。","part_of_speech":"名詞"},{"term":"leisure","translation":"余暇","definition":"仕事や義務から解放された自由な時間。","part_of_speech":"名詞"},{"term":"recuperation","translation":"回復","definition":"病気や疲労から元の状態に戻ること。","part_of_speech":"名詞"},{"term":"recreation","translation":"レクリエーション","definition":"娯楽やスポーツなど、心身をリフレッシュさせる活動。","part_of_speech":"名詞"},{"term":"downtime","translation":"ダウンタイム","definition":"機械やシステムが停止している時間；または、人がリラックスできる時間。","part_of_speech":"名詞"},{"term":"siesta","translation":"シエスタ","definition":"昼食後の短い昼寝（特にスペイン語圏）。","part_of_speech":"名詞"},{"term":"break","translation":"休憩","definition":"仕事や活動を一時的に中断すること。","part_of_speech":"名詞、動詞"},{"term":"nap","translation":"昼寝","definition":"短い睡眠。","part_of_speech":"名詞、動詞"}],"pronunciation":{"rest":"re-su-to","relaxation":"ri-ra-ku-se-shon","sleep":"su-i-min","vacation":"ba-ke-e-shon","holiday":"ho-ri-de-e","leisure":"re-jaa","recuperation":"ri-ku-pe-ra-shon","recreation":"re-ku-ri-e-e-shon","downtime":"da-un-ta-i-mu","siesta":"shi-e-su-ta","break":"bu-re-i-ku","nap":"na-pu"}}